methods.apply:
Apply this function to the input chunk, returning an output chunk.

 The result is owned by this Context.

:param input: io.deephaven.db.v2.sources.chunk.Chunk<? extends ToIntegerCast.T>
:return: (io.deephaven.db.v2.sources.chunk.IntChunk<? extends ToIntegerCast.T>) the result IntChunk
methods.makeToIntegerCast:
Create an IntFunctor that casts the values in an input chunk to an int.  An optional offset is applied to each
 value after the cast.

Note: Java generics information - <T extends io.deephaven.db.v2.sources.chunk.Attributes.Any>

:param type: io.deephaven.db.v2.sources.chunk.ChunkType
:param size: int
:param offset: int
:return: (io.deephaven.db.v2.hashing.ToIntFunctor<T>) a ToIntFunctor that can be applied to chunks of type in order to produce an IntChunk of values
